{"tid":931875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【二手蝕讓跳樓貨】泓景臺勁減480萬成交","createTime":"2018-12-07T10:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T15:25:22.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6eb22bce761fece1974fe1aae18ae1d449bd996d","tid":931875,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣地產周鍵喬透露，長沙灣泓景臺錄事故單位蝕讓，為2期7座中層戶，實用面積735方呎，三房套間隔。單位今年6月放盤，叫價1,380萬元，惟一直未有承接，日前大幅減價至900萬元終成功易手，累減480萬元，減幅35%，為同類型單位的市場新低價成交，呎價12,245元。<br />\n<br />\n據知，上址於今年3月發現跳樓事故，淪為凶宅。原業主2015年6月以929.6萬元買入上述單位，賬面虧損29.6萬元，跌幅約3%。<br />\n<br />\n周鍵喬補充，泓景臺現有約55個買賣盤提供，「入場費」由約850萬元起。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181207/59003803?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F59003803%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=J2lDsVeHwS0B9dU1HFKLq5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=68d94f64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F59003803%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=9d2d1fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181207/59003803?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a><br />\n<br />\n真跳樓貨"},{"pid":"cf8d30726357928983c57805a3996be75951ef06","tid":931875,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0607b33664e7ba894a3dca213ced9be6aa